{
  "1700270": {
    "name": "终极幸运之塔 (Lucky Tower Ultimate)",
    "steam_appid": 1700270,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冒险者，伊维留斯之塔正等着你——但，你真的确定自己不是来送人头的吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700270/extras/ea503276d6b0a129434ac407695d2c05.avif?t=1764095116\" width=600 height=100 /></span>《终极幸运之塔》是一场荒诞离奇的冒险，游戏的难度会让你直呼离谱，但你在被虐哭一百遍后，仍然会对着屏幕笑出猪叫。你会一次又一次被塔内的无情陷阱与凶悍怪物击倒，甚至鲜有机会踏出塔门，更别提抵达村庄。总之，别想着速通——先活着逃出塔再说吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700270/extras/89e878f166c4a89653113324e4c73078.poster.avif?t=1764095116\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700270/extras/89e878f166c4a89653113324e4c73078.webm?t=1764095116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700270/extras/89e878f166c4a89653113324e4c73078.mp4?t=1764095116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700270/extras/d13d663fc451f6843986af85867cef7d.avif?t=1764095116\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演自恋到无可救药的骑士 Von Wanst。你被光着膀子传送到了这座充满谜团的高塔，无依无靠、无路可循。你会沿途结识一群沙雕队友，获得他们的帮助和火力支援！每次扑街，你都会被踹回塔顶重开；每次重开，高塔结构都会改变，所以你的每趟旅程都独一无二。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《幸运之塔》鼓励玩家不断尝试、掌握技巧，还有从失败中汲取经验。面对谜题与敌人时，大胆实验，耐心摸索高塔中的各种机关与陷阱，方能逃出生天。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700270/extras/f4f34a9764e29681a46c59e9f42dff1b.poster.avif?t=1764095116\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700270/extras/f4f34a9764e29681a46c59e9f42dff1b.webm?t=1764095116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700270/extras/f4f34a9764e29681a46c59e9f42dff1b.mp4?t=1764095116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700270/extras/3cdcd807fd2a00263265e2515d6df831.avif?t=1764095116\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >终极幸运塔楼》是一项融合了闹剧幽默和手绘美学的 Roguelite 冒险挑战，每次挑战都仿佛置身于沉浸式的卡通世界。风格延续了一系列广受欢迎的经典 Flash 游戏，玩家要在三扇神秘门之间进行选择。《终极幸运塔楼》邀请新老玩家一同体验独一无二的游戏乐趣：即使做好了精心准备，也可能会因为踩上香蕉皮打滑而命丧黄泉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700270/extras/de3db1046988e2ae8ebe47cd0c99d976.poster.avif?t=1764095116\" width=800 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700270/extras/de3db1046988e2ae8ebe47cd0c99d976.webm?t=1764095116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700270/extras/de3db1046988e2ae8ebe47cd0c99d976.mp4?t=1764095116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700270/extras/f95bf2a0f64ebc8e9d5dede6cab8caa5.avif?t=1764095116\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中的所有物品，不论是西兰花还是死去的敌人，都可以被拾取并作为武器使用。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成功逃出塔楼后，你将抵达一个村庄——在这里可以进行交易、积累进度，打造属于自己的个性化家园</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全员戏精！惹毛队友，他们会和你翻脸；哄好反派，他们会为你开路</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过 200 件道具（既有黄金盔甲，也有喇叭…）以及超过 40 种阴间陷阱（蜂窝、炸药桶…）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1.0 版本将会更新真结局，与最终 Boss 决一死战——终极骑士的名号可不是白来的！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700270/extras/125e1dd4f22bd4b678efe2a354d0f5fa.poster.avif?t=1764095116\" width=780 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700270/extras/125e1dd4f22bd4b678efe2a354d0f5fa.webm?t=1764095116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700270/extras/125e1dd4f22bd4b678efe2a354d0f5fa.mp4?t=1764095116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700270/extras/34199f8b31a8e88fd635c9494753e383.avif?t=1764095116\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次游戏进程都会随机生成全新的关卡和发型，带来焕然一新的游戏体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >纯手绘 2D 卡通画风，沉浸感满满</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >震撼体验，爆笑连连。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多条逃生路线（包括阴间山洞）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >硬核但不上课（拒绝手把手教学）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >逃脱时带上同伴，还能解锁专属的伙伴任务线</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700270/extras/76dce9d33dfc84216e945a6969044703.poster.avif?t=1764095116\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700270/extras/76dce9d33dfc84216e945a6969044703.webm?t=1764095116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700270/extras/76dce9d33dfc84216e945a6969044703.mp4?t=1764095116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700270/extras/3b6032f09f8af790ec84fbb37fdaed74.avif?t=1764095116\" width=600 height=100 /></span><i>前往 Discord，了解游戏开发内幕。我们时不时会在 Discord 社区发布秘密游戏演示版本，如果您感兴趣，请一定要加入我们的 Discord 社区！</i> </p>",
